diagnosed</a> with <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anorexia_nervosa" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anorexia_nervosa" target="_blank">anorexia</a> when to everyone else it was blatantly obviousâOne even prescribed me appetiteincreasing pillsâBut trying to deal with her <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anorexia_nervosa" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anorexia_nervosa" target="_blank">anorexia</a> led to other problemsLydia said âI started <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drinking" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drinking" target="_blank">drinking</a> too which only fuelled my <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Appetite" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Appetite" target="_blank">appetite</a> and purging I would drink secretly in my room maybe two <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bottle" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bottle" target="_blank">bottles</a> of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wine" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wine" target="_blank">wine</a> a dayâMy parents found 40 <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bottle" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bottle" target="_blank">bottles</a> under my bed that I was hidingâAs she battled back from the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illness" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illness" target="_blank">illness</a> she <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Writing" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Writing" target="_blank">wrote</a> a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Book" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Book" target="_blank">book</a> Raw gives a powerful <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Insight" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Insight" target="_blank">insight</a> into life with an <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eating" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eating" target="_blank">eating</a> disorderShe said âI hope that others <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suffering" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suffering" target="_blank">sufferi